hadiths[46]{hadithnumber,text}:
1821,"mere walid suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) dushmanon ka pata lagaaney ( nikley. phir unke sathiyon ne to ehram baandh liya lekin) khud unhon-ne abhi ( nahi baandha tha ( asl mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi ne ye itlaa di thi ke maqam ghaiqa mein dushman aap ki taak mein hai, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( abu-Qatada aur chand sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko unki talash mein) rawaana kya mere walid ( abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) apne sathiyon ke sath they ke ye log aik doosrey ko dekh kar hansney lagey ( mere walid ne bayan kya ke) maine jo nazar uthai to dekha ke aik janglii gadhaa samney hai. main is par jhaptaa aur neze se usey thanda kar diya. maine apne sathiyon ki madad chahi thi lekin unhon-ne inkar kar diya tha, phir ham ne gosht khaayaa. ab hamein ye dar hua ke kahin (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) door na ho jaaein, chunanche maine aapko talash karna shuru kar diya kabhi apne ghodey tez kar deta aur kabhi aahista, aakhir raat gaey banu- ghifaar ke aik shakhs se mulaqat ho gaee. maine puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahan hain? unhon-ne bataya ke jab main aap se juda hua to aap maqam Ta'hin mein they aur aap ka irada tha ke maqam Saqeeya mein pahunch kar do-pahar ka aaraam karengey. gharaz main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya aur maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap ke ashaab aap par salam aur Allah ki rehmat bhejtey hain. unhein ye dar hai ke kahin wo bahut peechhey na reh jaaein. isliye aap thahar kar unka intizar karein, phir maine kaha ya Rasulullah! maine aik janglii gadhaa shikar kya tha aur uska kuchh bacha hua gosht ab bhi mere paas maujood hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se khaney ke liye farmaya halanke wo sab ehram baandhey huey they."
1822,"ham suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chaley unke sathiyon ne to ehram baandh liya tha lekin unka bayan tha ke maine ehram nahi baandha tha. hamein ghaiqa mein dushman ke maujood honey ki itlaa mili isliye ham unki talash mein (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke mutabiq ( nikley phir mere sathiyon ne gorkhar dekha aur aik doosrey ko dekh kar hansney lagey maine jo nazar uthai to usey dekh liya ghodey par) Sawar ho kar) is par jhaptaa aur usey zakhmi karke thanda kar diya. maine apne sathiyon se kuchh imdaad chahi lekin unhon-ne inkar kar diya phir ham sab ne usey khaya aur uske baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua (pahley ( hamein dar hua ke kahin ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se door na reh jayen isliye main kabhi apna ghoda tez kar deta aur kabhi aahista aakhir meri mulaqat aik banii-Ghifaar ke aadmi se aadhi raat mein hui maine puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahan hain? unhon-ne bataya ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ta'hin naam ke jagah mein alag hua tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irada ye tha ke do-pahar ko maqam Saqeeya mein aaraam karengey phir jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap ke ashaab ne aapko salam kaha hai aur unhein dar hai ke kahin dushman aap ke aur unke darmyan haail na ho jaey isliye aap unka intizar kijiye chunanche aap ne aisa hi kya, maine ye bhi kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! maine aik gorkhar ka shikar kya aur kuchh bacha hua gosht ab bhi maujood hai is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab se farmaya ke khaao halanke wo sab ehram baandhey huey they."
1823,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina se teen manzil door maqam qaaha mein they. (doosri sanad imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne) kaha ke ham se Ali-bin-Abdullaah ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Sufiyan ne bayan kya kaha ham se Saaleh-bin-Kaisaan ne bayan kya, unse abu-Muhammad ne aur unse abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam qaaha mein they, kuchh to ham mein se ehram ki haalat mein they aur kuchh ghair mahram. maine dekha ke mere sathi aik doosrey ko kuchh dikhaa rahe hain, maine jo nazar uthai to aik gorkhar samney tha, unki murad ye thi ke unka kodaa gir gaya, (aur apne sathiyon se usey uthaney ke liye unhon-ne kahaa), lekin sathiyon ne kaha ke ham tumhari kuchh bhi madad nahi kar saktey kyonke ham mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) hain) isliye maine wo khud uthaya iske baad main us gorkhar ke nazdeek aik teeley ke peechhey se aaya aur usey shikar kya, phir main usey apne sathiyon ke paas laayaa, kuchh ne to ye kaha ke (hamein bhi) kha lena chahiye lekin kuchh ne kaha ke nahi khana chahiye phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. aap ham se aagey they, maine aap se masla puchha to aap ne bataya ke kha lo ye halal hai. ham se Amr-bin-Dinar ne kaha ke Saaleh-bin-Kaisaan ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar us hadis aur uske ilawa ke mutaalliq poochh saktey ho aur wo hamarey paas yahan aaey they."
1824,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Haj ka ( irada karke nikley. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ki aik jamat ko jis mein abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they ye hidayat de kar rastey se wapas bheja ke tum log dariya ke kinarey kinaarey ho kar jao, (aur dushman ka pata lagaao ( phir ham se aa milo. chunanche ye jamat dariya ke kinaarey-kinaarey chalii, waapsii mein sab ne ehram baandh liya tha lekin abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne abhi ehram nahi baandha tha. ye qaafila chal raha tha ke kai gorkhar dikhai diye, abu-Qatada ne un par hamla kya aur aik maada ka shikar kar liya, phir aik jagah thahar kar sab ne uska gosht khaya aur sath hi ye khayal bhi aaya ke kya ham ehram ki haalat me honey ke bawajud shikar ka gosht bhi kha saktey hain? chunanche jo kuchh gosht bacha wo ham sath laey aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to kaha ya Rasulullah! ham sab log to ehram ki haalat me they lekin abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehram nahi baandha tha phir ham ne gorkhar dekhey aur abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne un par hamla karke aik maada ka shikar kar liya, iske baad aik jagah ham ne qiyam kya aur uska gosht khaya phir khayal aaya ke kya ham ehram ki haalat me honey ke bawajud shikar ka gosht kha bhi saktey hain? isliye jo kuchh gosht baqi bacha hai wo ham sath laey hain. aap ne puchha kya tum mein se kisi ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ko shikar karne ke liye kaha tha? ya kisi ne us shikar ki taraf ishara kya tha? sab ne kaha nahi. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir bacha hua gosht bhi kha lo."
1825,"jab wo Abwaa ya Wadaan mein they, to unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik gorkhar ka tohfa diya to aap ne usey wapas kar diya tha, phir jab aap ne unke chehron par narazagi ka rang dekha to aap ne farmaya waapsii ki wjah sirf ye hai ke ham ehram baandhey huey hain."
1826,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya panch janwar aisey hain jinhein maarney mein ehram waaley ke liye koi harj nahi hai.
1827,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ehram wala (panch janwaron ko) mar sakta hai. ( jinka zikr aagey aa raha hai).
1828,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke panch janwar aisey hain jinhein maarney mein koi gunah nahi kowa, cheel, choohaa, bichchhoo aur kaat khaney wala kuttaa."
1829,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya panch janwar aisey hain jo sab ke sab moozii hain aur unhein haram mein bhi maara ja sakta hai kowa , cheel , bichho , choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta ."
1830,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina ke ghaar mein they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par sura Mursalaat nazil honii shuru hui. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski tilawat karne lagey aur main aapki zaban se usey seekhney laga, abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tilawat khatm bhi nahi ki thi ke ham par aik sanp giraa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usey mar dalo chunanche ham uski taraf lapkey lekin wo bhag gaya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis tarah se tum iske shar se bach gaey wo bhi tumharey shar se bach kar chala gaya. (abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke us hadis se mera maqsad sirf ye hai ke Mina haram mein dakhil hai aur sahaba ne haram mein sanp maarney mein koi harj nahi samjha tha) ."
1831,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhipkalii ko moozii kaha tha lekin maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye nahi suna ke aap ne usey maarney ka bhi hukm diya tha.
1832,"jab Amr bin Saeed Makka par lashkar kashii kar raha tha to unhon-ne kaha ameer ijazat de to main aik aisi hadis sunaun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke doosrey din irshad farmai thi, us hadis Mubarak ko mere in kanon ne suna, aur mere dil ne poori tarah usey yad kar liya tha aur jab aap irshad farma rahe they, to meri aankhen aapko dekh rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur uski sana bayan ki, phir farmaya ke Makka ki hurmat Allah ne qaaim ki hai logon ne nahin! isliye kisi aisey shakhs ke liye jo Allah aur yaume-aakhirat par eman rakhta ho ye jaaiz aur halal nahi ke yahan khoon bahaaey aur koi yahan ka aik darakht bhi na kaatey lekin agar koi shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qitaal (fatah Makka ke mauqe par) se iska jawaz nikaley to us se ye keh do ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Allah ne ijazat di thi, lekin tumhen ijazat nahi hai aur mujhey bhi thodi si der ke liye ijazat mili thi phir dobara aaj uski hurmat aisi hi qaaim ho gaee jaisey pahley thi aur haan jo maujood hain wo ghayab ko (Allah ka ye paighaam) pahuncha dein, abu-Shuraih se kisi ne puchha ke phir Amr-bin-Saeed ne (ye hadis sun kar) aapko kya jawab diya tha? unhon-ne bataya ke Amr ne kaha abu-Shuraih! main ye hadis tum se bhi zyada janta hun magar haram kisi mujrim ko panah nahi deta aur na khoon karke aur na kisi jurm karke bhaagney waley ko panah deta hai. ( خربة ( se murad ( خربة بلية‏ ( hai."
1833,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala ne Makka ko hurmat wala banaya hai mujh se pahley bhi ye kisi ke liye halal nahi tha isliye mere baad bhi wo kisi ke liye halal nahi hoga. mere liye sirf aik din ghadi bhar halal hua tha isliye uski ghaas na ukhaadii jaey aur uske darakht na kaatey jaaein, iske shikar na bhadkaaye jayen aur na wahan ki giri hui cheez uthai jaey. haan elaan karne wala utha sakta hai. (taake asl Malik tak pahuncha de) Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! izkhir ki ijazat dijiye kyonke ye hamarey sunaaron aur hamari qabron ke liye kaam aati hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke izkhir ki ijazat hai. Khalid ne riwayat kya ke Ikrima (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke tum jantey ho ke shikar ko na bhadkaane se kya murad hai? iska matlab ye hai ke (agar kahin koi janwar saaye mein betha hua hai to) usey saaye se bhagaa kar khud wahan qiyam na kare."
1834,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya ab hijrat farz nahi rahi lekin) achi ( niyat aur jihad ab bhi baqi hai isliye jab tumhen jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to taiyaar ho jaanaa. us Shahar (Makka) ko Allah Taala ne isi din hurmat ata ki thi jis din us ne aasman aur zameen paida kiye, isliye ye Allah ki muqarrar ki hui hurmat ki wjah se mohtaram hai yahan kisi ke liye bhi mujh se pahley ladai jaaiz nahi thi aur mujhey bhi sirf aik din ghadi bhar ke liye (fatah Makka ke din ijazat mili thi) ab hamesha ye Shahar Allah ki qaaim ki hui hurmat ki wjah se qiyamat tak ke liye hurmat wala hai to iska kaantaa kaataa jaey na iske shikar haankey jayen aur us shakhs ke siwa jo elaan karne ka irada rakhta ho koi yahan ki giri hui cheez na uthaey aur na yahan ki ghaas ukhaadii jaey. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! izkhir (eik ghaas ( ki ijazat to dijiye kyonke yahan ye kaariigaron aur gharon ke liye zaroori hai to aapney farmaya ke izkhir ki ijazat hai."
1835,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ehram ki haalat mein they us waqt aap ne pachhna lagwaayaa tha. phir maine unhein ye kehtey suna ke mujh se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Taaus ne ye hadis bayan ki thi. us se maine ye samjha ke shayad unhon-ne un donon hazraat se ye hadis suni hogi (mutakallim Amr hain aur donon hazraat se murad ata aur Taaus (Rahmatullahi-alaih) hain) .
1836,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram ki haalat mein they apne sar ke beech mein maqam Lahiy-jamal mein pachhna lagwaayaa tha.
1837,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to aap ehram ki haalat mein they.
1838,"aik shakhs ne khadey ho kar puchha ya Rasulullah ! haalat ehram mein hamein kon se kapdey pahnney ki ijazat detey hain? to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke na qamees pahno na paajaamey , na amaamey aur na barans . agar kisi ke jootey na hon to mozon ko takhnon ke nichey se kaat kar pahan ley. isi tarah koi aisa libaas na pahno jis mein zafran ya waras laga ho. ehram ki haalat mein auratein munh par Naqaab na daalein aur dastaaney bhi na pahnein . Leis ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Musa-bin-Aqba aur Ismail bin Ibraaheem-bin-Aqba aur Juweriya aur ibne- Ishaq ne Naqaab aur dastaanon ke zikr ke silsiley mein ki hai. Ubaidullah (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne (aur waras nahin) ka lafz bayan kya wo kehtey they ke ehram ki haalat mein aurat munh par na Naqaab daley aur na dastaaney istemal karey aur Imam Malik ne Naafe se bayan kya aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke ehram ki haalat mein aurat Naqaab na daley aur Lais-bin-abii-Saleem ne Malik ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
1839,"aik mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) shakhs ke oont ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par uski gardan ( gira kar) tod di aur usey jaan se mar diya, us shakhs ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney laya gaya to aap ne farmaya ke unhein ghusl aur kafan de-do lekin unka sar na dhako aur na khushbu lagaao kyonke (qiyamat mein) ye labbaik kehtey huey uthega."
1840,"Abdullah-bin-Abbas aur miswar-bin-Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ka maqaame-Abwaa mein (eik mas'ale par) ikhtilaf hua. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan (mas'ala poochhney ke liye) bhejaa, main jab unki khidmat mein pahuncha to wo kunein ki 2 lakdiyon ke beech ghusl kar rahe they, aik kapdey se unhon-ne parda kar rakha tha maine pahunch kar salam kya to unhon-ne malum farmaya ke kon ho? maine kaha ke main Abdullaah-bin-Hunain hun, aap (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein mujhey Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bheja hai ye malum karne ke liye ke ehram ki haalat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar Mubarak kis tarah dhotey they. ye sun kar unhon-ne kapdey par (jis se parda tha) hath rakh kar usey nichey kya. ab aap ka sar dikhai de raha tha, jo shakhs unke badan par pani daal raha tha, us se unhon-ne pani dalney ke liye kaha, us ne unke sar par pani daalaa, phir unhon-ne apne sar ko donon hath se hilaayaa aur donon hath aagey le gaey aur phir peechhey laey farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (ehraam ki haalat mein) isi tarah kartey dekha tha."
1841,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Arafaat mein khutba detey suna tha ke jiske paas ehram mein jootey na hon wo mozey pahan ley aur jiske paas tehband na ho wo paa-jaama pahan ley.
1842,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke ehram ki haalat mein kon se kapdey pahan sakta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qamees, amaamaa, paa-jaama aur barans (kin top ya barish koot) na pahney aur na koi aisa kapda pahney jis mein zafran ya waras lagi ho aur agar jootiyaan na hon to mozey pahan ley, albatta is tarah kaat ley ke takhnon se nichey ho jaaein."
1843,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko maidaane-Arafaat mein waz (nasihat) sunaya, usmein aap ne farmaya ke agar kisi ko ehram ke liye tehband na miley to wo paa-jaama pahan ley aur agar kisi ko jootey na milein to wo mozey pahan ley."
1844,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zi-Qada mein Umra kya to Makka walon ne aapko Makka mein dakhil honey se rok diya, phir unse us shart par suleh hui ke hathiyar niyaam mein daal kar Makka mein dakhil hongey."
1845,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa ko meeqaat banaya, Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil ko aur Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam ko. ye meeqaat un mulkon ke baashindon ke liye hai aur doosrey un tamam logon ke liye bhi jawan mulkon se ho kar Makka aaein aur Haj aur Umre ka bhi irada rakhtey hon, lekin jo log un hudood ke andar hon to unki meeqaat wahi jagah hai jahan se wo apna safar shuru karein yahan tak ke Makka walon ki meeqaat Makka hi hai."
1846,fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka mein dakhil huey to aap ke sar par khod tha. jis waqt aap ne utara to aik shakhs ne khabar di ke ibne- khatal Kaba ke pardon se latak raha hai aap ne farmaya ke usey qatl kar do.
1847,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik shakhs jo jubba pahney huey tha hazir hua aur is par zardi ya isi tarah ki kisi khushbu ka nishan tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se kaha kartey they kya tum chahtey ho ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honey lagey to tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh sako? us waqt aap par wahi nazil hui phir wo haalat jati rahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis tarah apne Haj mein kartey ho isi tarah Umra mein bhi karo.
1848,"aik shakhs ne doosrey shakhs ke hath mein daant se kaataa tha, doosrey ne jo apna hath kheenchaa to uska daant ukhad gaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska koi badla nahi dilwaayaa."
1849,"maidaane-Arafaat mein aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath thehra hua tha ke apni ontni se gir padaa aur us ontni ne uski gardan tod daalii, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pani aur berii ke patton se usey ghusl do aur ehram hi ke 2 kapdon ka kafan do lekin khushbu na lagaanaa na iska sar chhipaanaa kyonke Allah Taala qiyamat mein usey labbaik kehtey huey uthaaega."
1850,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Arafaat mein thehra hua tha ke apni ontni se gir padaa aur usne uski gardan tod di, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pani aur berii se ghusl de kar do kapdon (ehraam walon hi mein) kafnaa do, lekin khushbu na lagaanaa, na sar chhipaanaa aur na Hanoot lagaanaa kyonke Allah Taala qiyamat mein usey labbaik pukaartey huey uthaaega."
1851,aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maidaane-Arafaat mein tha ke uske oont ne gira kar uski gardan tod di. wo shakhs ehram ki haalat mein tha aur mar gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye hidayat di ke usey pani aur berii ka ghusl aur (ehraam ke) 2 kapdon ka kafan diya jaey albatta usko khushbu na lagaao na uska sar chhipaao kyonke qiyamat ke din wo labbaik kehta hua uthega.
1852,"qabila Juhaina ki aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha ke meri walida ne Haj ki mannat maana thi lekin wo Haj na kar sakiin aur unka intiqal ho gaya to kya main unki taraf se Haj kar sakti hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, unki taraf se to Haj kar. kya tumhari maan par qarz hota to tum usey ada na kartiin? Allah Taala ka qarza to uska sabse zyada mustahiq hai ke usey pura kya jaey. to Allah Taala ka qarz ada karna bahut zaroori hai."
1853,"ham se abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha unse ibne-Shahab ne, unse Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne, unse Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Fazal-bin-Ayaaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke aik khatun .) hadis number 1854 dekhein ("
1854,Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par qabila Khash'am ki aik aurat aai aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ki taraf se fareeza Haj jo iske bandon par hai usne mere boodhey bap ko pa liya hai lekin unmein itni sakat nahi ke wo sawari par bhi baith sakein to kya main unki taraf se Haj kar loon to unka Haj ada ho jaaeyga? aap ne farmaya ke haan.
1855,"Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par peechhey baithey huey they. itney mein qabila Khash'am ki aik aurat aai. Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) usko dekhney lagey aur wo Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekhney lagi isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fazal ka chehra dusri taraf pherney lagey, us aurat ne kaha ke Allah ke fareeze ( Haj ( ne mere boodhey walid ko us haalat mein pa liya hai ke wo sawari par baith bhi nahi saktey to kya main unki taraf se Haj kar sakti hon, aap ne farmaya ke haan. ye Hijjatul-wada ka waqia hai."
1856,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Muzdalfa ki raat Mina mein saman ke sath aagey bhej diya tha.
1857,"main apni aik gadhi par Sawar ho kar (Minaa mein aaya (us waqt mein jawaanii ke qareeb tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein khadey Namaz padha rahe they. main pehli saf ke aik hissey ke aagey se ho kar guzra phir sawari se nichey utar aaya aur usey charney ke liye chhod diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey logon ke sath saf mein Sharik ho gaya, Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ke waaste se bayan kya ke ye Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Mina ka waqia hai."
1858,mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj karaya gaya tha. main us waqt saat (7) saal ka tha.
1859,Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saman ke sath (yani baal bachchon mein) Haj karaya gaya tha.
1860,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne aakhiri Haj ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ko Haj ki ijazat di thi aur unke sath Usman-bin-Affan aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja tha.
1861,"maine puchha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham bhi kyon na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad aur jangon mein jaya karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum logon ke liye sabse umda aur sabse munasib jihad Haj hai, wo Haj jo maqbool ho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin ke jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad sun liya hai Haj ko main kabhi chhodney wali nahi hun."
1862,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi aurat apne mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) rishtedar ke baghair safar na karey aur koi shakhs kisi aurat ke paas us waqt tak na jaey jab tak wahan koi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) maujood na ho. aik shakhs ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah! main falan lashkar mein jihad ke liye nikalnaa chahta hun, lekin meri biwi ka irada Haj ka hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to apni biwi ke sath Haj ko jaa."
1863,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada se wapas huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umme-Sanaan ansariya aurat (Raziallahu anhu) se malum farmaya ke to Haj karne nahi gaii? unhon-ne kaha ke falan ke bap yani mere khawind ke paas 2 oont pani pilaaney ke they aik par to khud Haj ko chaley gaey aur doosra hamari zameen sairaab karta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Ramazan mein Umra karna mere sath Haj karne ke barabar hai, is riwayat ko ibne-Juraij ne Ata se suna, kaha unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, aur Ubaidullah ne Abdul-Karim se riwayat kya, unse Ata ne unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
1864,"maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara jihad kiye they. wo kehtey they ke maine char baatein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thin ya ye ke wo ye char baatein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kartey aur kehtey they ke ye baatein mujhey intihai pasand hain ye ke koi aurat 2 din ka safar us waqt tak na karey jab tak uske sath iska shauhar ya koi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) na ho, na eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ke rozey rakhey jayen na Asr ki Namaz ke baad ghurub honey ke pahley aur na subah ki Namaz ke baad suraj nikalney se pahley koi Namaz padhi jaey aur na teen masaajid ke siwa kisi ke liye kajaawey baandhey jayen masjide-Haraam , meri masjid aur masjide-Aqsaa."
1865,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik boodhey shakhs ko dekha jo apne 2 beton ka sahara liye chal raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha un sahib ka kya haal hai? logon ne bataya ke unhon-ne Kaba ko paidal chalney ki mannat maana hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala us se be-niyaaz hai ke ye apne ko takleef mein daalein phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein sawar honey ka hukm diya.
1866,"Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya meri behan ne mannat maana thi ke Baitullah tak wo paidal jaaeingii, phir unhon-ne mujh se kaha ke tum iske mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi poochh lo chunanche maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo paidal chalein aur sawar bhi ho jaaein. Yazeed ne kaha ke abul-Khair hamesha Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath rahtey they."
